          <actionDate>2016-06-08</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong></strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense to design and produce an Atomic Veterans Service Medal to honor retired and former members of the Armed Forces who are radiation-exposed veterans.</p> <p>The<strong> </strong> Department may provide for issuance of the Medal to the next-of-kin of a deceased radiation-exposed veteran.</p>]]></text>
